description.narrative: DE Output 1(2014 - 2015). Technical assistance and support to ROs and COs to strengthen programming in child protection, across all contexts including humanitarian, which contributes to Policy, Guidance And Technical Support For Country Programming And Reporting, Prevention And Response Services For Violence Against Children. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Operational Support To Programme Delivery. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Strengthened programme to protect children from violence, exploitation, abuse and neglect in development and humanitarian settings
